headline: WM price target raised to $238 from $234 at Deutsche Bank
summary: Deutsche Bank analyst Faiza Alwy raised the firm’s price target on WM (WM) to $238 from $234 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The macro environment is expected to be favorable versus prior expectations in 2025 for the business and information services sector, the analyst tells investors in a research note. The firm says that while re-inflation is a risk, and yields have backed up, it remains optimistic with respect to the ability of business and info services companies to navigate challenge
